title: Fall Off the Wall!
itunes:title: Fall Off the Wall!
description: Today on the Cigar Authority, special guests Eric Hanson from Hammer & Sickle Vodkand Cigars, and Victor Vitale of the Cigar Agency Global Distribution stop by to bring us "The Berlin Wall"! Not the just the cigar, but the actual WALL itself! It's a show for the history books!
